HEADWORD: Zokor
<hw>Zo"kor</hw> <pr>(z⟦omac⟧"k⟦ocir⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An Asiatic burrowing rodent (<spn>Siphneus
